    "After the last imaging cycle, we added 80% formamide in 2x SSC buffer to remove RNAscope probes completely and stained the nuclei with 5 μM DRAQ5 at room temperature for 10 min.",
    "RNAscope data processing.",
    "RNAscope data was processed with the DART-FISH pipeline with one modification.",
    "The images from the \"Empty\" cycle were subtracted from all RNAscope images to remove the autofluorescence.",
    "The DART-FISH datasets were processed by our custom pipeline."
